<main class="container">
    <section class="card">
        <h2>Same-Day Delivery</h2>
        <p><b>Same-day delivery is available under the following conditions:</b></p>
        <ul>
            <li>The purchased items are ON HAND.</li>
            <li>The order is successfully paid.</li>
            <li>The delivery address is within Metro Manila.</li>
            
        </ul>
        <p><b>Orders that do not meet these conditions will be processed as standard delivery.</b></p>
        <h2>Process:</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Customers must book a delivery service at their own expense.</li>
            <li>Booking is available until 5:00 PM.</li>
            <li>Use your preferred delivery app and input the provided pickup information.</li>
           <li>Include your name or order number in the rider notes.</li>
            
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
        <h2>Standard Delivery</h2>
        <div class="info-group">
            <ul>
                <li><b>Metro Manila:</b> 2-7 working days</li>
                <li><b>Provincial Areas:</b> 3-12 business days</li>
                <li><b>Pre-order items:</b> 30 days</li>
               <li>Delivery costs are paid by the customer and depend on the delivery location and items in the order.</li>
               <li>Orders with multiple items will be shipped together once all items are available.</li>
               <li>Processing is done Monday to Friday, from 9:00 AM to 3:00 PM.</li>
               <li>Delivery times may be delayed due to high order volumes or stock availability.</li>
                
            </ul>
    </section>
        

    <section class="card">
        <h2>Payment Options</h2>
        <p><b>The following payment methods are available depending on the product's condition:</b></p>
        <li>E-Wallet.(GCASH)</li>
        <li><b>Note:</b> Cash-on-Delivery (COD) is not accepted.</li>
        
    </section>

   
    
